# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# For more information: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/platform/redirects/

# SPA Routing - Redirect all routes to index.html for client-side routing
# The 200 status code serves the file without changing the URL
/* /index.html 200

# Optional: Add any specific redirects here (uncomment and modify as needed)
# Example: Redirect old URLs to new ones
# /old-path /new-path 301
# /blog/* /news/:splat 301

# Example: External redirects
# /docs https://docs.example.com 301

# Example: API proxy (if you need to proxy API requests)
